text.div:
This code system https://example.org/fhir/CodeSystem/PatientGenderStatus defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
neutered NeuteredThe animal has been sterilized, castrated or otherwise made infertile.
intact IntactThe animal's reproductive organs are intact.
unknown Unknown Unable to determine whether the animal has been neutered.

name: PatientGenderStatus
title: Patient Gender Status Code System
description: This code system defines the status of a patient's gender.
purpose: This FHIR resource type CodeSystem has been created for educational purposes.

concept.definition: The animal has been sterilized, castrated or otherwise made infertile.
The animal's reproductive organs are intact.
Unable to determine whether the animal has been neutered.
